abstract: Seatwave, a startup that creates a secondary market for theater, sports and music event tickets in Britain and Europe, is expected to announce on Monday that it has raised $25 million in a series C round of fundraising.
lead_paragraph: Seatwave, a startup that creates a secondary market for theater, sports and music event tickets in Britain and Europe, is expected to announce on Monday that it has raised $25 million in a series C round of fundraising.
